OL,3,C'It's more like a care home': The
OL,4,Cprison struggling with an ageing
OL,5,Cpopulation
OL,7,FITV News Scotland Reporter Louise
OL,8,FScott was given exclusive access
OL,9,Finside Glenochil jail in Alloa where
OL,10,F10% of the population is over 60
OL,12,FPrisons across the UK are struggling
OL,13,Fto cope with increasing numbers.
OL,15,FShort term emergency release has given
OL,16,Fsome institutions breathing room, but
OL,17,Ffor many, it barely scratches the
OL,18,Fsurface.
