OL,3,C'It's more like a care home': The
OL,4,Cprison struggling with an ageing
OL,5,Cpopulation
OL,7,FGlenochil prison in Scotland houses a
OL,8,Fhigh number of sex offenders and those
OL,9,Fserving life sentences, meaning many
OL,10,Fare growing old within their walls.
OL,12,FIt's putting extreme pressure on an
OL,13,Falready overstretched system.
OL,15,FAfter months of arranging, we were
OL,16,Fgiven exclusive access inside
OL,17,FGlenochil, to a hall housing sex
OL,18,Foffenders and murderers.
OL,20,FWhat followed, was like nothing I've
OL,21,Fever witnessed inside a prison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
