OL,3,C'It's more like a care home': The
OL,4,Cprison struggling with an ageing
OL,5,Cpopulation
OL,7,F"We had one recently that just passed
OL,8,Faway a couple of weeks ago, he was
OL,9,Fwell in his late 80s. We're not a
OL,10,Fhospital, we're not a care home, but
OL,11,Fit's getting more and more like a care
OL,12,Fhome."
OL,14,FAt Glenochil there is 24/7 agency
OL,15,Fsocial care staff working alongside
OL,16,Fthe officers.
OL,18,FColin Dougall is from Ailsa Care and
OL,19,Fsaid doing the job within prison is
OL,20,Fmuch more challenging due to the size
OL,21,Fof cells they work within.
