OL,3,C'It's more like a care home': The
OL,4,Cprison struggling with an ageing
OL,5,Cpopulation
OL,7,F"If they have something like dementia,
OL,8,Fthey can sometimes kick off at any
OL,9,Fmoment but that's why we have our
OL,10,Fofficers."
OL,12,FThe idea of a prison care home has
OL,13,Fbeen raised, which would mean a
OL,14,Fdedicated place for older prisoners to
OL,15,Fbe looked after.
