OL,3,C'It's more like a care home': The
OL,4,Cprison struggling with an ageing
OL,5,Cpopulation
OL,7,FThe cost of this social care is
OL,8,Fcrippling for the Prison service. In
OL,9,FScotland alone it rose from #636,000
OL,10,Fin 2018 to #2,877,000 last year.
OL,11,FThat's a 450% increase in a little
OL,12,Fmore than five years.
OL,14,FThat's down to the rising population
OL,15,Fof older prisoners. In Scotland over
OL,16,F50s has jumped from an average of 612
OL,17,Fin 2010 to 1419 last year.
