OL,3,C'It's more like a care home': The
OL,4,Cprison struggling with an ageing
OL,5,Cpopulation
OL,7,FGlenochil's Governor Sharanne Findlay
OL,8,Fsaid: "We have an average of 80 people
OL,9,Fover the age of 60 and that's in a
OL,10,Fpopulation of just over 700, so
OL,11,Fthere's a significant number of people
OL,12,Fwho are older.
OL,14,F"When prisons were designed and built,
OL,15,Fthey didn't generally have an older
OL,16,Fpopulation in mind. Most of the
OL,17,Festablishment is built for younger,
OL,18,Ffitter people.
