OL,3,C'It's more like a care home': The
OL,4,Cprison struggling with an ageing
OL,5,Cpopulation
OL,7,FIn terms of the difference that would
OL,8,Fmake, Sharanne said: "I think the less
OL,9,Fpeople we have in prison, the more we
OL,10,Fcan we look after the people who
OL,11,Freally do need to be in prison. And in
OL,12,Fturn, it's all about reducing risk and
OL,13,Freleasing people back into the
OL,14,Fcommunity."
OL,16,FBut some would argue, these prisoners
OL,17,Fshould be serving their entire
OL,18,Fsentence locked up, whether it's
OL,19,Fsuitable or not.
