OL,3,C'It's more like a care home': The
OL,4,Cprison struggling with an ageing
OL,5,Cpopulation
OL,7,FInevitably that would improve social
OL,8,Fcare for prisoners, which some may
OL,9,Ffind hard to swallow when many
OL,10,Fvulnerable older members in the
OL,11,Fcommunity are often unable to access
OL,12,Fsuch support.
OL,14,FBut emergency release isn't doing
OL,15,Fenough to alleviate the issue of
OL,16,Fovercrowding in prisons, and many of
OL,17,Fthe older inmates do not need to be in
OL,18,Fsuch a secure facility.
