OL,3,C'It's more like a care home': The
OL,4,Cprison struggling with an ageing
OL,5,Cpopulation
OL,7,F"We have made clear that we need take
OL,8,Fa measured and considered look at how
OL,9,Fbest our prison estate can respond to
OL,10,Fthe challenges posed by the complex
OL,11,Fnature of the population particularly
OL,12,Fgiven its significance increase in
OL,13,Frecent times.
OL,15,F"This includes being cognisant of our
OL,16,Fageing population and the need to
OL,17,Fensure our prison estate is fit for
OL,18,Fpurpose and provides a range of
OL,19,Fsupport to help reduce reoffending and
OL,20,Faid integration back into the
OL,21,Fcommunity."
